# Miscellaneous

### rotationEquivalenceRelationsHold — Rotation Equivalence Relations Hold

Rotation equivalence relations hold: asserts `ROTL`{n} x == ROTR`{(w - n) % w} x` and `ROTR`{n} x == ROTL`{(w - n) % w} x` for all `x`.

**Involved:** [`ROTL`](../functions/ROTL.md), [`ROTR`](../functions/ROTR.md)

The Cryptol block below gives the exact Cryptol property checked by verification.

<details><summary>Formal property (Cryptol)</summary>

```cryptol
left && right where
left = ROTL`{n} x == ROTR`{(w - n) % w} x
right = ROTR`{n} x == ROTL`{(w - n) % w} x
```

</details>

### hexDigitsEncodeCorrectly — Hex Digits Encode Correctly

Hex digits encode correctly: asserts `0x7 == 0b0111` and `0xa == 0b1010`.

The Cryptol block below gives the exact Cryptol property checked by verification.

<details><summary>Formal property (Cryptol)</summary>

```cryptol
(0x7 == 0b0111) && (0xa == 0b1010)
```

</details>

### wordsEncodeCorrectly — Words Encode Correctly

Words encode correctly: asserts `0xa103fe23 == 0b10100001000000111111111000100011` and `0xa103fe2332ef301a == 0b1010000100000011111111100010001100110010111011110011000000011010`.

The Cryptol block below gives the exact Cryptol property checked by verification.

<details><summary>Formal property (Cryptol)</summary>

```cryptol
short && long where
short = 0xa103fe23 == 0b10100001000000111111111000100011
long = 0xa103fe2332ef301a == 0b1010000100000011111111100010001100110010111011110011000000011010
```

</details>

### integersEncodeCorrectly — Integers Encode Correctly

Integers encode correctly: asserts `291 == 0x00000123`.

The Cryptol block below gives the exact Cryptol property checked by verification.

<details><summary>Formal property (Cryptol)</summary>

```cryptol
291 == 0x00000123
```

</details>
